    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer16235708" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4257065570001645530">I read this book when it first came out. I always knew the Willie and Martin Handcart companies had a tough time coming across the plains, but this book made me feel like I was there! I have a great-aunt that was part of the trek and hearing her story told in this book was heart wrenching to feel what those people went through.<br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

